482" Left="283" Right="283" Top="482"/><PARALIST LineWrap="Break" LinkListID="0" LinkListIDNext="0" TextDirection="0" VertAlign="Center"><P ParaShape="5" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="23"><CHAR>신체나 체위를 가끔 변경시킬 수 있지만, 자주·많이 변경하지는 못한다.</CHAR></TEXT></P></PARALIST></CELL></ROW><ROW><CELL BorderFill="6" ColAddr="1" ColSpan="3" Dirty="false" Editable="false" HasMargin="true" Header="false" Height="2064" Protect="false" RowAddr="18" RowSpan="1" Width="8187"><CELLMARGIN Bottom="283" Left="283" Right="283" Top="283"/><PARALIST LineWrap="Break" LinkListID="0" LinkListIDNext="0" TextDirection="0" VertAlign="Center"><P ParaShape="5" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="23"><CHAR>약간 제한됨</CHAR></TEXT><TEXT CharShape="24"/></P></PARALIST></CELL><CELL BorderFill="6" ColAddr="4" ColSpan="3" Dirty="false" Editable="false" HasMargin="true" Header="false" Height="2064" Protect="false" RowAddr="18" RowSpan="1" Width="1838"><CELLMARGIN Bottom="0" Left="0" Right="0" Top="0"/><PARALIST LineWrap="Break" LinkListID="0" LinkListIDNext="0" TextDirection="0" VertAlign="Center"><P ParaShape="4" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="23"><CHAR>3</CHAR></TEXT></P></PARALIST></CELL><CELL BorderFill="6" ColAddr="7" ColSpan="8" Dirty="false" Editable="false" HasMargin="true" Header="false" Height="2064" Protect="false" RowAddr="18" RowSpan="1" Width="31900"><CELLMARGIN Bottom="482" Left="283" Right="283" Top="482"/><PARALIST LineWrap="Break" LinkListID="0" LinkListIDNext="0" TextDirection="0" VertAlign="Center"><P ParaShape="5" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="23"><CHAR>조금이기는 하지만 혼자서 신체나 사지의 체위를 자주 변경시킨다.</CHAR></TEXT></P></PARALIST></CELL></ROW><ROW><CELL BorderFill="33" ColAddr="1" ColSpan="3" Dirty="false" Editable="false" HasMargin="true" Header="false" Height="2064" Protect="false" RowAddr="19" RowSpan="1" Width="8187"><CELLMARGIN Bottom="283" Left="283" Right="283" Top="283"/><PARALIST LineWrap="Break" LinkListID="0" LinkListIDNext="0" TextDirection="0" VertAlign="Center"><P ParaShape="5" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="23"><CHA